.container
    .jumbotron.subhead
        %h1
            = @page_title = "Modules"
    %section
        .row
            = partial('modules_sidebar')
            .col-sm-9
                .page-header
                    %h1= @page_sub_title = "Gamerules"
                :markdown
                    Minecraft's built in game rules can be set via the `<gamerules>` module. Not all gamerules are supported, the table below lists which are supported.

                    When stopping the daylight cycle, you should either use the `<doDaylightCycle>` gamerule, or the [timelock](/modules/other_settings#timelock) element.  One will overwrite the other, so be consistent.

                .table-responsive
                    %table.table.table-striped.table-condensed
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Element
                                %th Description
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %span.highlight
                                        %code= html_escape('<gamerules> </gamerules>')
                                %td Node containing the defined game rules.

                %h5 Supported Gamerule Sub-elements
                .table-responsive
                    %table.table.table-striped.table-condensed
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Element
                                %th Description
                                %th Values
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %span.highlight
                                        %code= html_escape('<doFireTick>')
                                %td Toggles whether firespread occurs.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true / false
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %span.highlight
                                        %code= html_escape('<doTileDrops>')
                                %td Toggles whether tile entities drop.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true / false
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %span.highlight
                                        %code= html_escape('<doMobLoot>')
                                %td Toggles whether mobs drop loot on death.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true / false
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %span.highlight
                                        %code= html_escape('<mobGriefing>')
                                %td Toggles whether mobs such as Creepers and Endermen cause enviromental damage.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true / false
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %span.highlight
                                        %code= html_escape('<naturalRegeneration>')
                                %td Toggles whether or not players naturally regain heath.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true / false
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %span.highlight
                                        %code= html_escape('<doDaylightCycle>')
                                %td Toggles whether or not the time tick occurs.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true / false


                :markdown
                    Example

                        <gamerules>
                            <doDaylightCycle>false</doDaylightCycle>
                            <naturalRegeneration>false</naturalRegeneration>
                        </gamerules>


                %br
                %h5 Unsupported Gamerules
                .table-responsive
                    %table.table.table-striped.table-condensed
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Rule
                                %th Reason
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code doMobSpawning
                                %td
                                    Not supported in favor of the
                                    %a{:href => "/modules/mobs"} mobs
                                    module.
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code keepInventory
                                %td Not supported since PGM already solves this with kits.
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code commandBlockOutput
                                %td Command blocks are disabled in PGM.
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code logAdminCommands
                                %td Not useful in custom maps.
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code randomTickSpeed
                                %td Not useful in custom maps.
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code reducedDebugInfo
                                %td Not useful in custom maps.
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code sendCommandFeedback
                                %td Not useful in custom maps.
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code showDeathMessages
                                %td Not useful in custom maps.
